{
    "title": "Things Have Changed",
    "artist": "Bob Dylan",
    "composer": "Bob Dylan / Marlon Mcvey / Preetesh Hirji",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n[Intro] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am2\">Am2</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n\n\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A worried man with a worried mind</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">No one in front of me and nothing behind</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>                                               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">There's a woman on my lap and she's drinking champagne</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Got white skin, got assassin's eyes</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I'm looking up into the sapphire tempered skies</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>                           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I'm well dressed, waiting on the last train</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>                               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Standin' on the gallows with my head in the noose</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>                                              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Any minute now I'm expectin' all hell to break loose</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">People are crazy and times are strange</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I'm locked in tight, I'm out of range</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I used to care but - things have changed</span>\n\n( <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span> )\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">This place ain't doin' me any good</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I'm in the wrong town, I should've been in Hollywood</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>                                               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Just for a second there I thought I saw something move</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Gonna take dancin' lessons, do the jitterbug rag</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ain't no shortcuts, gonna dress in drag</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>                           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Only a fool in here would think he got anythin' to prove</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>                               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Lotta water under the bridge, lotta other stuff too</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>                                              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Don't get up gentlemen, I'm only passing through</span>\n\n( <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span> )\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I've been walkin' forty miles of bad road</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">If the Bible is right the world will explode</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>                                               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I'm tryin' to get as far away from myself, as I can</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Some things are too hot to touch</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">The human mind can only stand so much</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>                           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">You can't win, with a losing hand</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>                               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Feel like falling in love, with the first woman I meet</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>                                              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Puttin' her in a wheelbarrow, and wheelin' her down the street</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I hurt easy, I just don't show it</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">You can hurt someone and not even know it</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>                                               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">The next sixty seconds could be like an, eternity</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Gonna get lowdown, gonna fly high</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">All the truth in the world adds up to one big lie</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>                           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I'm in love with a woman that don't even appeal to me</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>                               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mr. Jinx and miss Lucy they jumped in a lake</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>                                              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I'm not that eager to make a mistake</span>\n",
